1
00:01:00,018 --> 00:01:01,519
This is crazy.

2
00:01:01,603 --> 00:01:03,313
But it was so good.

3
00:01:03,396 --> 00:01:04,606
I couldn't stop it.

4
00:01:07,358 --> 00:01:09,110
I want to keep sleeping like this.

5
00:01:09,694 --> 00:01:10,737
Me too.

6
00:01:12,572 --> 00:01:14,115
Should we just skip school today?

7
00:01:58,701 --> 00:02:01,746
At least if I was drunk,
I could have used that as an excuse.

8
00:02:06,709 --> 00:02:11,381
EPISODE 4: I KNOW IT ISN'T LOVE.
NEVERTHELESS,

9
00:02:16,928 --> 00:02:17,887
Ouch!

10
00:02:18,805 --> 00:02:21,307
-Are you okay?
-Oh yeah, I'm fine.

11
00:02:21,391 --> 00:02:23,434
Uh, do you know where's the hairdryer is?

12
00:02:24,227 --> 00:02:25,103
Damn it.

13
00:02:25,186 --> 00:02:26,521
Could we talk for a second?

14
00:02:28,356 --> 00:02:30,441
Oh! Hey, hey, put a shirt on!

15
00:02:34,237 --> 00:02:36,781
Whoa, I must have
alcohol-related dementia.

16
00:02:37,282 --> 00:02:39,701
I don't remember anything
that happened yesterday.

17
00:02:40,326 --> 00:02:42,162
-So maybe--
-It was all a mistake?

18
00:02:42,245 --> 00:02:43,079
What?

19
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:47,292
Oh…

20
00:02:47,876 --> 00:02:51,337
Yeah. Honestly, we both
made a mistake. We were drunk, right?

21
00:02:52,297 --> 00:02:55,341
Since we made a mistake,
nothing has to change between us.

22
00:02:56,092 --> 00:02:57,177
Don't you think?

23
00:02:57,677 --> 00:02:58,761
I'm gonna go now.

24
00:02:59,429 --> 00:03:01,097
Hey! Wait!

25
00:03:01,639 --> 00:03:02,765
Hey!

26
00:03:07,312 --> 00:03:10,190
Oh! Damn it! What have I done?

27
00:03:10,940 --> 00:03:14,360
I must have lost my mind!
Why did it have to be him?

28
00:03:23,203 --> 00:03:24,495
Wait, is that mine?

29
00:03:25,288 --> 00:03:28,666
Yeah. I, uh, washed it for you.

30
00:03:29,792 --> 00:03:31,127
It's fine, you can have it.

31
00:03:32,253 --> 00:03:33,296
Or just throw it away.

32
00:03:34,881 --> 00:03:37,383
Oh, I'm going out to have breakfast.

33
00:03:38,051 --> 00:03:39,219
Out?

34
00:03:39,302 --> 00:03:40,511
By myself.

35
00:03:41,679 --> 00:03:44,891
Oh, right. I totally get it.

36
00:03:45,558 --> 00:03:47,602
I should get some more sleep.

37
00:03:48,311 --> 00:03:49,520
Go ahead.

38
00:03:54,192 --> 00:03:55,818
I really want to keep seeing you.

39
00:03:57,862 --> 00:03:58,738
What about you?

40
00:03:59,322 --> 00:04:00,823
This is it, Na-bi.

41
00:04:00,907 --> 00:04:01,741
What do you mean?

42
00:04:02,325 --> 00:04:03,701
Can we meet up again sometime?

43
00:04:04,285 --> 00:04:05,703
Okay, so let me get this straight.

44
00:04:05,787 --> 00:04:07,872
Even if we're not dating right now,

45
00:04:07,956 --> 00:04:10,917
he's asking me if I want to meet up and…

46
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,710
sleep with him from time to time?

47
00:04:13,586 --> 00:04:15,004
I'm not sure.

48
00:04:16,214 --> 00:04:17,548
Think about it and tell me.

49
00:04:18,299 --> 00:04:21,636
I'll be off. Go to the hospital
if you feel sick. Okay?

50
00:04:23,471 --> 00:04:24,305
Mm-hm.

51
00:04:49,038 --> 00:04:50,331
Park Jae-eon?

52
00:05:06,764 --> 00:05:09,726
-Last night wasn't a mistake for me.
-What?

53
00:05:09,809 --> 00:05:12,979
And things won't be the same
for me, either. Not anymore.

54
00:05:13,062 --> 00:05:15,815
I don't think I can just pretend
it didn't happen.

55
00:05:21,779 --> 00:05:23,114
So what's going to happen now?

56
00:05:23,197 --> 00:05:25,908
I really don't think that I can just
stay friends with you now,

57
00:05:25,992 --> 00:05:27,076
after everything we did.

58
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,536
What are you…

59
00:05:30,663 --> 00:05:32,957
-You don't mean…
-I want you to be my girlfriend.

60
00:05:38,421 --> 00:05:40,173
Hey!

61
00:05:41,049 --> 00:05:42,467
You…

62
00:05:44,260 --> 00:05:46,554
You want me to be your girlfriend
because we slept together once?

63
00:05:46,637 --> 00:05:48,723
Don't you think you're overreacting?

64
00:05:48,806 --> 00:05:50,016
Do… do you like me?

65
00:05:53,686 --> 00:05:56,230
There. See? You can't even answer that.

66
00:05:56,314 --> 00:05:59,233
Besides, I really don't want to date
within such a small department,

67
00:05:59,317 --> 00:06:01,277
because rumors
are going to spread so fast.

68
00:06:01,361 --> 00:06:03,029
And it's going to be really annoying.

69
00:06:07,658 --> 00:06:08,659
All right.

70
00:06:09,869 --> 00:06:13,206
I understand how you feel,
so I'll take care of my feelings.

71
00:06:13,790 --> 00:06:15,708
Hmm… What do you mean? Hey!

72
00:06:16,626 --> 00:06:17,627
Hey!

73
00:06:21,547 --> 00:06:24,425
The guy Sol brought over last night,
was he her boyfriend?

74
00:06:25,510 --> 00:06:26,594
I don't know.

75
00:06:30,056 --> 00:06:32,266
You're the only one here
who'd know! Come on!

76
00:06:32,350 --> 00:06:34,519
Just who is that guy? And is it…

77
00:06:37,522 --> 00:06:39,065
Is it serious?

78
00:06:39,857 --> 00:06:42,026
Why don't you go and ask her yourself?

79
00:06:42,110 --> 00:06:44,862
I don't care who she dates.
So stop asking me.

80
00:06:44,946 --> 00:06:45,863
It's so annoying.

81
00:06:46,531 --> 00:06:49,033
Wh-what happened? Did you two fight?

82
00:06:51,285 --> 00:06:55,164
Oh, right. You also didn't know
Sol's going to be an exchange student.

83
00:06:55,248 --> 00:06:58,126
We didn't fight. That's just
the extent of our relationship.

84
00:06:59,127 --> 00:07:00,169
I'm leaving.

85
00:07:14,142 --> 00:07:15,309
Seo Ji-wan.

86
00:07:16,227 --> 00:07:18,938
Ji-wan. Ji-wan!

87
00:07:19,730 --> 00:07:21,149
Let me talk to you.

88
00:07:24,026 --> 00:07:26,529
Fine. Let's talk.
So, where do you wanna start?

89
00:07:26,612 --> 00:07:29,407
Going abroad? Or maybe your new boyfriend?

90
00:07:29,490 --> 00:07:31,701
Everyone knew about it, except me.

91
00:07:31,784 --> 00:07:33,411
Come on, I was going to tell you.

92
00:07:33,494 --> 00:07:35,913
Oh. And when were you going to tell me?

93
00:07:35,997 --> 00:07:38,666
The day before you leave?
The day before you get married? When?

94
00:07:38,749 --> 00:07:41,544
What's with you? You said
you don't care who I date, remember?

95
00:07:41,627 --> 00:07:43,963
Right. I couldn't care less.
I'm just angry with you,

96
00:07:44,046 --> 00:07:45,798
because you're leaving me
out of everything like this.

97
00:07:45,882 --> 00:07:48,801
-Oh, when did I ever leave you out of--
-You're always doing this, Sol.

98
00:07:48,885 --> 00:07:51,721
You never tell me about
the important things in your life.

99
00:07:51,804 --> 00:07:53,014
You know that?

100
00:07:54,974 --> 00:07:56,100
Like what, Ji-wan?

101
00:08:09,655 --> 00:08:13,201
I guess this is really the extent
of our relationship.

102
00:08:38,226 --> 00:08:39,393
Thank you.

103
00:08:41,354 --> 00:08:42,688
What's your next class?

104
00:08:43,606 --> 00:08:46,275
Human Anatomy. It's really hard.

105
00:08:47,276 --> 00:08:48,945
I actually got an A in that class.

106
00:08:49,028 --> 00:08:50,363
-Wait, really?
-Mm.

107
00:08:50,446 --> 00:08:51,739
Then help me study for the exam.

108
00:08:51,822 --> 00:08:53,157
What will you do for me?

109
00:08:58,037 --> 00:08:59,497
What should I do for you?

110
00:09:01,832 --> 00:09:03,000
Jeez…

111
00:09:07,004 --> 00:09:09,966
Oh, uh… by the way…

112
00:09:11,926 --> 00:09:13,052
Um…

113
00:09:14,178 --> 00:09:18,391
I don't want, uh, anyone to know about us.
So can we keep this a secret?

114
00:09:20,851 --> 00:09:23,229
All right. My lips are sealed.

115
00:09:24,021 --> 00:09:25,231
-Mm.
-Hmm.

116
00:09:26,566 --> 00:09:28,359
And, also…

117
00:09:29,193 --> 00:09:30,152
Um…

118
00:09:31,153 --> 00:09:32,488
You don't, uh…

119
00:09:34,323 --> 00:09:38,536
have any… di… diseases, do you?

120
00:09:41,872 --> 00:09:43,040
Do you?

121
00:09:44,959 --> 00:09:48,296
Hey, don't laugh! I'm really serious.

122
00:09:49,630 --> 00:09:51,382
No, I don't, so don't worry.

123
00:09:53,759 --> 00:09:54,594
Mm.

124
00:09:56,637 --> 00:09:58,306
Do you have time later?

125
00:10:00,308 --> 00:10:02,935
Yes, I, uh… I have some time.

126
00:10:03,019 --> 00:10:05,438
Oh, no, wait. Should we meet on Saturday?

127
00:10:06,939 --> 00:10:08,733
You need to rest the next day, right?

128
00:10:10,401 --> 00:10:11,485
Oh, no.

129
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:14,113
It's totally fine, I'm all right.

130
00:10:48,064 --> 00:10:51,359
Why in the world did I do that?
I was so impulsive.

131
00:10:52,902 --> 00:10:54,945
I must've lost my mind.

132
00:11:00,159 --> 00:11:02,286
I should just tell him not to come here.

133
00:11:18,803 --> 00:11:20,721
-Come in.
-Hmm.

134
00:11:27,353 --> 00:11:29,480
-What's with the beer?
-Uh…

135
00:11:30,064 --> 00:11:31,982
I thought it'll be nice to drink together.

136
00:11:32,066 --> 00:11:33,359
You know, to spice things up.

137
00:11:34,318 --> 00:11:36,779
Oh, I already drank some earlier.

138
00:11:36,862 --> 00:11:39,532
I couldn't do this sober.

139
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:42,868
This is cheating, you know.

140
00:11:43,452 --> 00:11:44,328
What do you mean?

141
00:11:45,871 --> 00:11:48,082
We, uh, didn't really decide on anything.

142
00:11:49,625 --> 00:11:50,501
Decide on what?

143
00:11:51,335 --> 00:11:54,797
Weren't we… going to study
human anatomy together?

144
00:11:56,382 --> 00:11:57,967
Oh.

145
00:11:59,427 --> 00:12:01,470
Right. Human anatomy.

146
00:12:03,097 --> 00:12:05,099
Yes. We should study.

147
00:12:10,646 --> 00:12:12,064
Stop laughing already.

148
00:12:14,275 --> 00:12:15,359
I have a gift for you.

149
00:12:25,619 --> 00:12:27,788
Jae-eon is so smooth with everything.

150
00:12:28,873 --> 00:12:32,668
It's like everything
just comes so naturally to him.

151
00:12:33,252 --> 00:12:34,754
There, all done.

152
00:12:38,841 --> 00:12:39,842
Do you like it?

153
00:12:41,427 --> 00:12:42,428
Mm.

154
00:12:44,805 --> 00:12:46,015
It's so pretty.

155
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:50,269
When the sun shines through it
in the morning, it'll be much prettier.

156
00:13:01,071 --> 00:13:02,448
Here we go again.

157
00:13:03,449 --> 00:13:05,367
Like this was always
going to happen between us.

158
00:13:10,915 --> 00:13:12,500
You got me once again.

159
00:13:18,172 --> 00:13:19,215
Hang on a second.

160
00:13:25,012 --> 00:13:26,597
PARK JAE-EON

161
00:13:29,225 --> 00:13:30,601
You saved my number.

162
00:13:32,812 --> 00:13:33,729
Mm.

163
00:13:37,191 --> 00:13:38,901
I should stop this right now.

164
00:13:40,736 --> 00:13:44,698
Because there are so many reasons
why I shouldn't do this.

165
00:13:49,328 --> 00:13:50,538
But…

166
00:14:14,562 --> 00:14:16,272
Did you know you have a mole here?

167
00:14:17,314 --> 00:14:18,148
Really? Where?

168
00:14:19,149 --> 00:14:20,150
Right here.

169
00:14:23,946 --> 00:14:25,197
No, I didn't know.

170
00:14:30,077 --> 00:14:33,038
Today you look… so much prettier.

171
00:14:33,122 --> 00:14:35,916
Even at this moment,
I'm still attracted to him.

172
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:39,295
Like crazy.

173
00:15:00,774 --> 00:15:02,651
And that one simple reason,

174
00:15:04,069 --> 00:15:06,614
buries all my worries
and makes me forget them.

175
00:15:12,119 --> 00:15:15,748
Didn't it hurt when you got
that tattoo behind your neck?

176
00:15:18,834 --> 00:15:20,461
Yeah, of course it hurt.

177
00:15:21,629 --> 00:15:23,005
I almost died that day.

178
00:15:25,174 --> 00:15:26,884
I thought of quitting in the middle of it.

179
00:15:31,305 --> 00:15:33,098
I'm gonna get another one soon.

180
00:15:34,266 --> 00:15:35,392
Where?

181
00:15:39,730 --> 00:15:41,106
Somewhere here.

182
00:15:43,859 --> 00:15:44,985
Another butterfly?

183
00:15:45,569 --> 00:15:46,612
Mm-hm.

184
00:15:48,280 --> 00:15:51,909
It'll be a butterfly
with lots of black spots on its wings.

185
00:15:51,992 --> 00:15:53,410
The name's pretty long.

186
00:15:54,119 --> 00:15:57,665
Taiwanese black-star hairstreak butterfly.

187
00:16:00,084 --> 00:16:01,210
Taiwan…

188
00:16:02,378 --> 00:16:03,879
That is a long name.

189
00:16:07,716 --> 00:16:09,593
You know, when they're still caterpillars,

190
00:16:10,135 --> 00:16:12,680
they don't actually eat leaves,
they eat flowers instead.

191
00:16:13,806 --> 00:16:15,099
Pretty unique, right?

192
00:16:16,976 --> 00:16:17,977
Mm.

193
00:16:19,061 --> 00:16:22,356
Since that day, a lot of things
have changed between us.

194
00:16:23,148 --> 00:16:26,402
And just like that,
Jae-eon slowly seeped into my life.

195
00:16:31,782 --> 00:16:33,158
Go take a shower.

196
00:16:41,917 --> 00:16:43,919
I'm starting my job at the department.

197
00:16:44,003 --> 00:16:46,922
You decided to do that? Aren't you busy?

198
00:16:47,006 --> 00:16:49,967
I'm not gonna work that long.
It's just for a little while.

199
00:16:50,801 --> 00:16:51,969
Hmm.

200
00:16:53,387 --> 00:16:54,555
It's all because of you.

201
00:16:57,891 --> 00:16:58,976
Why? What did I do?

202
00:17:00,936 --> 00:17:02,271
Come visit me, okay?

203
00:17:03,355 --> 00:17:04,189
And why should I?

204
00:17:04,273 --> 00:17:05,524
-Hmm?
-Hmm?

205
00:17:07,234 --> 00:17:08,610
Just come visit me.

206
00:17:10,320 --> 00:17:11,363
Just do it, okay?

207
00:17:12,114 --> 00:17:13,282
Why should I?

208
00:17:15,534 --> 00:17:17,036
All right, I will.

209
00:17:23,459 --> 00:17:26,462
Jae-eon, where's the suncatcher
you made last time?

210
00:17:26,962 --> 00:17:30,049
-The butterfly-shaped one.
-Oh, that thing?

211
00:17:31,258 --> 00:17:32,551
I gave it to someone.

212
00:17:32,634 --> 00:17:36,096
Aw. That's too bad. I wanted to see it
when it was finished.

213
00:17:36,180 --> 00:17:38,015
Hey, Jae-eon,
tell us how to make the suncatcher.

214
00:17:38,098 --> 00:17:39,183
Yeah! Tell us!

215
00:17:39,266 --> 00:17:41,435
Just talk to Ceramics and Glass students.

216
00:17:41,518 --> 00:17:43,479
Learn that from them. Jae-eon is mine now.

217
00:17:43,562 --> 00:17:44,688
Right?

218
00:17:44,772 --> 00:17:47,399
What are you going on about?

219
00:17:47,483 --> 00:17:48,817
You're so nosy!

220
00:17:49,485 --> 00:17:52,696
If you're done, and have nothing
to do here, please leave.

221
00:17:53,530 --> 00:17:55,949
Did you hear me? Huh? Get out.

222
00:17:56,033 --> 00:17:57,451
-Okay!
-We're leaving now.

223
00:17:57,534 --> 00:17:58,786
-Bye-bye.
-See ya!

224
00:18:01,205 --> 00:18:04,333
I heard that he doesn't date,
but I guess he has a girlfriend.

225
00:18:04,416 --> 00:18:06,752
I wonder who it is.
She must be really pretty.

226
00:18:23,894 --> 00:18:25,938
-It's been raining a lot.
-Hmm.

227
00:18:35,322 --> 00:18:36,865
-Don't do it.
-I have to do this!

228
00:18:37,866 --> 00:18:40,119
All right, stop working. Let's just sleep.

229
00:18:40,661 --> 00:18:41,995
-Already?
-Mm-hm.

230
00:18:44,206 --> 00:18:45,958
-Really?
-I'm sleepy.

231
00:18:54,466 --> 00:18:58,720
Our relationship
only exists at night, but…

232
00:19:00,222 --> 00:19:01,932
Are you washing the dishes?

233
00:19:02,015 --> 00:19:05,227
Yeah. It looks like you don't do
the dishes when I'm coming.

234
00:19:05,310 --> 00:19:07,062
You caught me.

235
00:19:07,688 --> 00:19:09,940
Although, I think you're actually
pretty good at housework.

236
00:19:10,732 --> 00:19:11,900
Will you do the laundry too?

237
00:19:13,277 --> 00:19:15,279
-Should I do it?
-Yes.

238
00:19:15,362 --> 00:19:16,905
Let's do it together.

239
00:19:16,989 --> 00:19:19,408
No, I don't want to.
I don't wanna do it.

240
00:19:19,491 --> 00:19:23,120
It sometimes felt like
he and I were lovers.

241
00:19:23,829 --> 00:19:25,414
What's your goal today?

242
00:19:27,374 --> 00:19:29,001
Ooh…

243
00:19:29,084 --> 00:19:30,544
Can you really do it?

244
00:19:32,629 --> 00:19:34,089
Don't strain yourself, okay?

245
00:19:40,095 --> 00:19:41,096
What was that, Jae-eon?

246
00:19:43,307 --> 00:19:46,643
Whenever I eat this,
my tongue would always feel numb.

247
00:19:47,352 --> 00:19:48,645
That's why I kissed you first.

248
00:19:48,729 --> 00:19:51,815
Jae-eon is still a mystery to me.

249
00:19:51,899 --> 00:19:53,192
You're crazy.

250
00:19:53,275 --> 00:19:54,568
-Let's eat.
-Okay.

251
00:19:56,236 --> 00:19:57,404
Here.

252
00:19:59,865 --> 00:20:00,699
Mmm.

253
00:20:01,617 --> 00:20:05,704
You said your tongue goes numb
when you eat this. But it's good.

254
00:20:05,787 --> 00:20:06,997
-Really?
-Mm-hm.

255
00:20:13,170 --> 00:20:14,880
Just eat.

256
00:20:18,800 --> 00:20:20,385
-Mmm.
-It's good, right?

257
00:20:20,469 --> 00:20:22,554
It's tastier today.

258
00:20:43,867 --> 00:20:47,120
I can't tell if he's kind or cold,

259
00:20:47,996 --> 00:20:50,958
or whether he's serious or joking.

260
00:21:05,305 --> 00:21:06,556
Are you done with assignments?

261
00:21:07,766 --> 00:21:08,976
Not yet.

262
00:21:10,102 --> 00:21:11,728
You should go home and sleep there.

